[news reporter] Investigations
are still underway.

04:52.040 --> 04:53.610
As of yet there are
no suspects,

04:53.660 --> 04:55.366
and the owner
of the plantation says

04:55.420 --> 04:56.990
there have been
no direct threats.

04:57.040 --> 04:58.371
I cant believe this.

04:58.420 --> 04:59.830
So disrespectful.

04:59.880 --> 05:01.450
What do you mean?

05:01.510 --> 05:03.410
I mean, I get it.

05:03.470 --> 05:06.086
Ive seen lots of people
disrespecting over there, but...

05:06.140 --> 05:08.461
but thats still history,
you know?

05:08.510 --> 05:10.341
If they wanted
to make a statement,

05:10.390 --> 05:12.130
they should have just
burned down the big house.

05:14.770 --> 05:16.931
Oh, were still studying for
my physics test after school.

05:16.980 --> 05:18.686
Yes. Yes, we are.

05:18.730 --> 05:19.890
You keep ditching
our study sessions.

05:19.940 --> 05:21.100
I know, Im sorry.

05:22.940 --> 05:24.646
I see my girls.

05:24.700 --> 05:26.406
Okay.

05:26.450 --> 05:28.941
-Have a good day.
-You too.

05:28.990 --> 05:30.901
[school bell rings]

05:30.950 --> 05:32.747
Im not stupid.
I didnt tell them nothing.

05:32.790 --> 05:34.701
Gave them the exact alibi
everybody else gave.

05:34.750 --> 05:36.365
-Are you sure?
-Yes.

05:36.420 --> 05:38.126
Cops were at his house
last night.

05:38.170 --> 05:39.990
-Whose house?
-Ants.

05:40.040 --> 05:42.668
-Are you serious, bro?
-Yeah.

05:42.710 --> 05:44.917
But they dont got nothing.
Its just because of the game.

05:44.970 --> 05:46.676
People are talking.

05:46.720 --> 05:49.962
Its all over the news,
the Internet.

05:50.010 --> 05:51.591
Its going to be okay.

05:51.640 --> 05:53.767
You find it or not?
Its my pops.

05:53.810 --> 05:55.346
Oh, it was just probably
in someones bag.

05:55.390 --> 05:57.267
-We|| find it.
-Man, I hope so.

05:57.310 --> 05:58.686
Going to need it.

06:01.190 --> 06:03.818
I know Jarretts being
all thorough and everything.

06:03.860 --> 06:06.738
But, Lord,
some of these.

06:06.780 --> 06:11.365
Aint nobody going to put a pie
shop in the middle of nowhere.

06:11.410 --> 06:12.729
Look”.

06:15.410 --> 06:18.072
Baby, are you all right?

06:18.120 --> 06:21.203
I think I just slept
on my neck wrong last night.

06:21.250 --> 06:24.629
-Oh. I got me some aspirin.
-No, Im good. Im good.

06:24.670 --> 06:27.127
Im about to just take this out
to the truck and move on out.

06:30.220 --> 06:32.097
All right now.
Love you.

06:32.140 --> 06:33.630
I love you too.

06:47.900 --> 06:50.027
Whatever youve got,

06:50.070 --> 06:53.574
I can assure you
my wife already knows.

06:53.620 --> 06:56.657
Thats not why I asked you here,
Cokon.

06:58.870 --> 07:01.532
You might have my cousin
wrapped around your finger,

07:01.580 --> 07:04.993
but let me be clear:
theres a bIg difference

07:05.050 --> 07:07.166
between a Boudreaux
and a Landry.

07:09.380 --> 07:12.429
You got five minutes.
What do you want?

07:14.220 --> 07:16.677
Your shares in
Landry Enterprises.

07:16.720 --> 07:18.631
All 10%.

07:20.560 --> 07:21.800
Ill double
what youve paid her.

07:23.940 --> 07:25.510
Keep your mistress.

07:27.650 --> 07:31.154
No, Im here because of
a company called Pillary Reach.

07:31.200 --> 07:33.816
Now, youve been
rolling around in the mud

07:33.870 --> 07:35.826
with your frat brothers.

07:35.870 --> 07:37.940
Washing everyones
dirty money

07:38.000 --> 07:39.444
through your little
shell company.

07:40.910 --> 07:43.287
Its a "good ole boy" clich.

07:43.330 --> 07:46.163
But Daddy will not be happy
when he finds out.

07:48.340 --> 07:50.126
Ill give you half.

07:50.170 --> 07:51.831
Now, 5% is a lot.

07:51.880 --> 07:54.713
Money laundering
is a federal crime, Colton.

07:56.260 --> 07:57.670
And not only will you
go to prison,

07:57.720 --> 08:01.383
but the painstaking
FBI searches

08:01.440 --> 08:03.055
and all the investigations

08:03.100 --> 08:05.148
into your daddys
companies and finances,

08:05.190 --> 08:07.897
everything youve ever
been a part of...

08:09.440 --> 08:11.567
hell regret ever
giving you a dime.

08:15.700 --> 08:16.906
I want it all.

08:18.240 --> 08:20.242
All 10%.

08:20.290 --> 08:21.951
Im not here to barter.

08:27.840 --> 08:32.334
You can take your daddy down,
or I can take you down.

08:32.380 --> 08:34.041
Your choice.

08:43.100 --> 08:44.897
-[door opens and closes]
-[exhales]

08:46.060 --> 08:47.857
[knock on door]

08:47.900 --> 08:50.061
Finish your homework.

08:56.570 --> 08:58.071
[sighs]

09:00.450 --> 09:01.826
Are you Ralph Angel Bordelon?

09:03.790 --> 09:05.360
Whats this about?

09:05.420 --> 09:07.126
My name is Lorena Campos,

09:07.170 --> 09:10.048
This is Nina Williams
and Officer Charbonneau.

09:10.090 --> 09:12.251
Were from the Department
of Child and Family Services.

09:12.300 --> 09:14.165
Can we talk inside?

09:14.220 --> 09:16.711
Yall cant just be rolling up
on people like that.

09:16.760 --> 09:18.921
Sir, if we could please
just step inside.

09:18.970 --> 09:20.255
It wont take long.

09:22.720 --> 09:24.130
Come on.

09:40.030 --> 09:42.737
[Nina] And what did you have
for breakfast this morning?

09:42.790 --> 09:45.577
Eggs, toast and milk.

09:45.620 --> 09:47.076
[recorder beeps]

09:47.120 --> 09:48.951
We was in a rush
this morning.

09:49.000 --> 09:51.161
Kitchen usually
would be clean.

09:51.210 --> 09:53.792
I want to make sure
you finish reading through.

09:53.840 --> 09:55.580
-[Nina] Who made breakfast?
-[B|ue] Pop made it.

09:55.630 --> 09:57.837
Did Pop take you
to school too?

09:57.880 --> 10:00.178
Yes.

10:00.220 --> 10:03.178
Do you wake your pop up,
or does he wake you up?

10:03.220 --> 10:06.383
For school,
he wakes me up.

10:06.440 --> 10:09.147
On the weekend,
I wake him up.

10:09.190 --> 10:12.148
I see. Have you ever not
been able to wake your pop up?

10:13.780 --> 10:15.520
No.

10:15.570 --> 10:17.561
No. Okay.

10:20.320 --> 10:23.153
I just got to say,

10:23.200 --> 10:25.407
watching you
living this dream,

10:25.450 --> 10:27.077
standing up for yourself,

10:27.120 --> 10:30.419
all you Bordelons
are just so strong.

10:30.460 --> 10:32.951
I read that essay about
your brother this morning.

10:33.000 --> 10:35.457
That niece of yours
is a damn good writer.

10:35.510 --> 10:37.080
That she is,

10:37.130 --> 10:39.121
but what you mean
you read about Ernest?

10:39.180 --> 10:42.547
I printed it out after
my sister found it online,

10:42.600 --> 10:44.386
and she asked me
if these Bordelons

10:44.430 --> 10:46.512
was related
to Miss Violet.

10:46.560 --> 10:49.051
You know, and I was just glad
to read some good in the world

10:49.100 --> 10:50.476
instead of that awful fire.

10:50.520 --> 10:51.976
-You hear about that?
-I did.

10:54.940 --> 10:58.103
New Yorker.
Thats big, aint it?

10:58.150 --> 10:59.526
It sure is.

11:07.330 --> 11:09.150
Lets talk
about your record.

11:09.210 --> 11:12.748
My record got nothing to do
with my ability to be a dad.

11:12.790 --> 11:14.587
My interest is in your record
as it pertains

11:14.630 --> 11:16.245
to the welfare
of your child.

11:16.300 --> 11:18.757
Nothing wrong with
the welfare of my child.

11:18.800 --> 11:21.542
He fine.
Scraped his arm at school.

11:21.590 --> 11:24.423
And thats it.

11:24.470 --> 11:26.461
I need you to pay
attention here, please.

11:26.520 --> 11:28.670
Its kind of hard when she
in there interrogating my kid.

11:28.730 --> 11:30.595
This is standard
procedure.

11:30.640 --> 11:33.143
Who called you, huh?
I want to know.

11:33.190 --> 11:35.226
We cant disclose
that information.

11:35.270 --> 11:37.602
Look, Im a good dad, okay?

11:37.650 --> 11:41.108
I work my ass off
taking care of that boy.

11:41.150 --> 11:44.313
I provide for my son,
make sure he eat.

11:44.370 --> 11:46.656
Always safe, happy.

11:48.700 --> 11:51.749
I aint do nothing wrong,
all right?

11:51.790 --> 11:53.781
I aint do nothing wrong,
you understand?

11:53.830 --> 11:55.741
And, yeah, I want to know,

11:55.790 --> 11:58.293
who the hell said
I aint a good dad, huh?

11:58.340 --> 12:00.046
Why dont you sit down.

12:00.090 --> 12:02.923
Let us do our jobs
and well be on our way.

12:19.320 --> 12:20.685
Prosper?

12:20.740 --> 12:22.196
[Prosper]
Im in here.

12:23.490 --> 12:24.696
