12:26.530 --> 12:28.441
Here. Take my hand.

12:29.740 --> 12:31.458
Are you okay?

12:31.500 --> 12:34.116
-I just need a little help.
-Okay. Okay.

12:34.170 --> 12:36.240
Here, lets...
lets get you up.

12:38.090 --> 12:39.626
