[dialing]

13:49.410 --> 13:50.980
-Good morning.
-Good morning.

13:51.030 --> 13:52.736
So you have to just
put your name there,

13:52.790 --> 13:54.906
and the company,
and the date and floor.

13:54.960 --> 13:57.076
[cell phone vibrates]

14:00.750 --> 14:02.661
-Thank you.
-Have a good day.

14:02.710 --> 14:04.291
Hello?

14:04.340 --> 14:06.251
So you think Im an unfit daddy,
huh?

14:06.300 --> 14:07.756
What are you
talking about?

14:07.800 --> 14:09.085
You tell me.

14:09.140 --> 14:10.755
I just had a cop

14:10.800 --> 14:12.631
and two ladies
from Child Services up here.

14:12.680 --> 14:14.671
They say somebody
filed a complaint.

14:14.720 --> 14:17.132
-What? _
-Wanna tell me whats gomg on?

14:17.190 --> 14:18.646
