I got eyes on him.
Hes in the east hallway.

15:08.860 --> 15:10.816
-You Anthony Coleman?
-Yeah.

15:12.280 --> 15:13.986
[Micah]
Yo, man, get off...

15:14.030 --> 15:15.486
He has a right to know
what this about.

15:15.540 --> 15:18.077
Back up, young lady.

15:18.120 --> 15:20.668
Anthony Coleman, youre under
