be used against you...

15:32.590 --> 15:33.966
[school bell rings]

15:41.650 --> 15:43.390
All right.

15:43.440 --> 15:45.010
So, I understand youre here
to see Kevin Jarvis?

15:45.070 --> 15:46.890
-Yes, maam.
-Hes out.

15:46.940 --> 15:48.817
My names Taj Clemens.

15:48.860 --> 15:50.942
What can I do for you,
Mr....?

15:50.990 --> 15:52.696
Bordelon.

15:55.240 --> 15:59.199
